{"tid":159943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大量殉職唔好問點解] 警方嚴厲譴責暴亂人士 對判刑表示歡迎","createTime":"2017-03-17T11:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T11:50:25.000Z","uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1ea1270a24863229d2808083269879cdee8bd43","tid":159943,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"旺角騷亂中首宗暴動案件，三被告被裁定罪成今被判入獄三年，有組織罪案及三合會調查科總督察陳純青庭外表示，警方對判刑及定罪表示歡迎。陳指法官於判刑時已指出當晚不少同袍生命受威脅，未有受傷實屬幸運，而陳補充當晚受傷的警員數目不少於103人。陳對當晚的暴亂人士作出嚴厲譴責，強調香港警方就算面對多大困難，定必堅定不移，緊守崗位，以專業態度執行職務。<br />\n<br />\n陳說畢後即被身旁的女警拉走，在場亦有記者隨即提出詢問，惟陳僅轉身叫記者「你問返PPRB（警察公共關係科）」。"},{"pid":"6688119cf50fcfc90253cbf6ce710acc652981c2","tid":159943,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a2ec7ba3db2078307d820bed9d49e280749432","tid":159943,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5870d11242527622f6aefbc25acc0c2b14a8f532","tid":159943,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"政治中立？我屌你老母冚家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd483a0c8ef05a5980fc3b0f360b9a22d9637c4","tid":159943,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:50:25.000Z","msg":"但點解冇啦啦搵條友出黎做發言人<br />\n9UP完先話搵PPRB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}